notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-22T13:06:54.204Z",claude-code-agent,"Implemented src/core/extensions/activation-summary.ts: describeExtensionActivation(activation, {extensionName?}) -> ExtensionActivationSummary. Pure function, walks every sub-registry the loader populates (same surfaces capability-usage attributes), returns flat sorted/deduped identifier arrays for all 16 surfaces + capabilities (reusing collectUsedExtensionCapabilities). Re-exported from sdk/index.ts barrel AND sdk/testing.ts subpath (barrel identity locked via toBe in the spec). KEY findings: (1) registerMigration allows id-less migrations -> migrations field uses a narrowing flatMap (cast-free, the empty-array branch is reachable+covered); (2) importer/exporter command paths land in commands.handlers but NOT registrations.commands unless command-metadata options are passed -> commands vs command_handlers genuinely differ, documented in interface JSDoc + test. 7 new tests in tests/unit/core/extensions/activation-summary.spec.ts (full-surface, flag dedup, union+filter, no-match-empty, id-less migration, empty activation, barrel identity). 100% line/branch/func/stmt on the module. Documented in docs/SDK.md (Testing Helpers prose + Public Exports + Common types). Full suite: 4850 tests green, 100/100/100/100 coverage. Manual temp-dir verify: real package imported describeExtensionActivation from @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk/testing, activated, got full surface + filter in one call."
body: ""
